        "name": "Rigid Form",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "You utilize wood's rigidity to prevent harmful shapechanging effects. For the duration of this spell, whenever you're targeted by a harmful polymorph effect, you can use your reaction to attempt to counteract the effect.",
